s='value-change'><h3>PhoenixRepair 的代码已在 GitHub 公开</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;https://github.com/DeepSoftwareAnalytics/PhoenixRepair&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18859' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>在 SWE-bench-Verified 上，PhoenixRepair 在 DeepSeek-V3.1 下相对 SWE-agent 取得 7.8% 的最大相对提升</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>7.8</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18859' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>实验评测在 SWE-bench-Verified 基准上进行</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;SWE-bench-Verified&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18859' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>PhoenixRepair 流程为多位置采样（困难任务可选引入基于图的定位信息）、迭代反思与优化生成更优补丁，并由历史尝试提炼的洞见指导终轮生成</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;multi-location sampling -&gt; iterative reflection and refinement -&gt; final-round generation guided by distilled insights&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18859' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>现有基于智能体的方法在修复策略探索上存在两点根本性不足：对多个潜在编辑位置的探索有限，以及对每个位置修复尝试的探索也不充分</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;limited exploration of multiple edit locations and insufficient exploration of repair attempts per location&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18859' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>GAIA基准上DeepDebug修复后整体准确率为63.6%。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>63.6</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18754' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>GAIA基准上三个解耦自纠错基线单次重跑修复的失败任务数为4至6个。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>{&quot;max&quot;: 6, &quot;min&quot;: 4}</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18754' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>AgentDebugX将调试组织为「检测—归因—恢复—重跑」闭环，并通过Python库、CLI、Web控制台和可安装的agentic skill暴露工作流，附带可选的Error Hub用于共享脱敏失败诊断修复包。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;Detect-Attribute-Recover-Rerun closed loop exposed via Python library, CLI, web console, and installable agentic skill, with opt-in Error Hub&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18754' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>Who and When基准上最强单轮基线的严格归因准确率为21.7%。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>21.7</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.18754' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>arxiv.org ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>DeepDebug在Who and When基准上、qwen3.5-9b骨干上取得28.8%严格智能体与步骤精确匹配率，最强单轮基线为21.7%。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态